Sentencas: We report a simple synthesis of La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 nanorods (LSM-R) through hydrothermal reaction followed by calcination at high temperature (700-850 degrees C).
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: Thermogravimetric analysis and XRD study reveals that 850 degrees C is adequate for phase pure LSM-R formation.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: The microstructure of the powder has been clinically studied using FESEM and TEM.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: It is observed that the intermediate hydrothermal treatment plays key role in formation of such nanorods.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: Different bulk properties of LSM-R like sinteractivity, CTE, density, electrical conductivity etc. have been comprehensively studied.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: A maximum electrical conductivity of around 250 S/cm at 800 degrees C is obtained when LSM-R specimen is sintered at 1200 degrees
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology
Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: The cathodic polarization of such LSM-R is measured using impedance analysis.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: It is observed that polarization value initially decreases attains minimum and then starts to increase with increase in cathode sintering temperature and dwelling time.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology

Sentencas: A minimum cathodic polarization value of 0.32 Omega/cm(2) at 800 degrees C is obtained at an optimized cathode sintering condition of 1000 degrees C/2 h. (C) 2017 Hydrogen Energy Publications LLC.
Titulo: Improved polarization behaviour of nanostructured La0.65Sr0.3MnO3 cathode with engineered morphology
